**The data includes:**
- your fiscal code;
- the email address you provided and, if applicable, confirmation that it has been validated;
- the text of the messages you have received;
- your notification preferences.

The information will be downloaded in YAML format, a standard format used in computing that allows for the exchange of data between different applications.

You will receive a **message on IO** containing a link and a password that are valid for 15 days.

For more information, see the **[IO Privacy Policy.](privacy://policy)**
